{"tid":1448284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非全面進場］反警暴遊行勢在必行！清算黑警暴行！","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:56:06.000Z","uid":277187,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4c92b01c8b96d0840459df8349668ac484c236ee","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"721元朗事件係前提<br />\n呢兩個月以嚟，尤&middot;其&middot;是&middot;今&middot;晚！！！<br />\n25歲女示威者失去咗一隻眼！面骨碎裂！因為黑警開槍！<br />\n扮示威者混入人群製造混亂！<br />\n尖沙咀街頭近距離開槍狙擊示威者！<br />\n喺葵芳大量施放催淚氣體導致居民不適！<br />\n都仲未講佢班仆街用過期催淚氣體！<br />\n太古城地鐵站1米內開槍射擊人群！<br />\n喺扶手電梯高危地方瘋狂追打示威者！！<br />\n仲用削尖竹支嫁禍示威者！<br />\n<br />\n除咗要大講警察嚴重暴力行為、濫捕問題<br />\n仲要提醒大眾警黑合作係一直存在！<br />\n今日警察喺後巷同啲紅衫講嘅野<br />\n叫佢地返去涼冷氣好聲好氣招呼佢地<br />\n大把證據指證佢地同黑社會合作！<br />\n唔好忘記仲有721專題鏗鏘集！！！<br />\n<br />\n黑警嘅惡行罄竹難書<br />\n唔可以只靠勇武派去以武制暴<br />\n況且今晚大量送頭<br />\n和理非一定要企出嚟清算黑警暴行！！！<br />\n幫班手足攞返個公道！<br />\n<br />\n我地必須以反警暴、反警黑合作為前提<br />\n號召一場大型嘅遊行！！！<br />\n而家全香港18區都食勻催淚彈<br />\n係時候去搞一場最少200萬人參與嘅和理非回合<br />\n誓要清算黑警<br />\n對準721警黑合作嘅死穴打落去！！！<br />\n<br />\n幫推呀！！！"},{"pid":"0d2116a991ea69c3f6507fb752dec13a60ddbfff","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:09.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"803b74ea66c410470545ce32386af895ee576975","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ca60edbf8767647e2a5a8f3240f9aa176adf71","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204663cfddb84eb94aa50528a7d56e00fc20f2b0","tid":1448284,"uid":130302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"639be6a0a40f5b50f4505c6d30647dcf3c1d33f5","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"dc6e5e70d7449e0804e9d51d8ac5924b56395391","tid":1448284,"uid":130302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"聽日一點機場等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610e14d6350ed7f3231d9caff6f47878c91c77f7","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:50.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"f89b2ae376b19d30e0e4cc6cf9957c4a3c61c148","tid":1448284,"uid":130302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:50.000Z","msg":"聽日一點機場等"},{"pid":"52d7f8c7c5822e0aa600c578d7c723852d177533","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f89b2ae376b19d30e0e4cc6cf9957c4a3c61c148","tid":1448284,"uid":130302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:50.000Z","msg":"聽日一點機場等"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"機場好重要！仲要再有一個和理非回合呀！！"},{"pid":"51a46dd8cd308eb6151a7ab5c74a0f50951a3e37","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:41.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"9c99f890f0f9557db6dfe0bbf0707d6980d388d5","tid":1448284,"uid":210912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8441242e99ab962731c9a73e787265bda2fd8c4","tid":1448284,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"民陣係時候出動啦<br />\n唔好又膠化啲口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1bc6fa37dce7743149f89f6b618ba90bf59339","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"推到民陣做野！"},{"pid":"c5744ea6c0a8a292710f1def3461f0de2ea2ee5d","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"反警仲要向班犬去申請不反對通知書簡直笑話一樣！屌你！好撚嬲！"},{"pid":"3aec7d4983b5d45b2b81618d15dba486d9b6a14d","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:01.000Z","msg":"轉載由羅冠聰: <br />\n<br />\n8月11號，極度心痛的一日。黑警濫權施暴的程度史無前例地誇張，毫無顧忌地犯下戰爭罪行，再次證明現存制度是不可能讓他們得到任何懲處。喪盡天良。<br />\n<br />\n黑警罪行：<br />\n<br />\n。向示威者頭部問槍，有人被布袋彈射中右眼，最新消息為右眼球破裂，永久失明。<br />\n<br />\n。向救護員開槍，有救護員疑似被射至昏迷。救護員需要舉旗警告黑警停止攻擊，以免犯下戰爭罪行。<br />\n<br />\n。插贓嫁禍示威者，將木竹及膠管等攻擊性武器放在示威者的背囊。<br />\n<br />\n。向遠在天橋的記者瘋狂開槍，有記者中催淚彈槍。<br />\n<br />\n。鄉黑攻擊記者時，黑警在旁袖手旁觀，並護送施襲者離開。<br />\n<br />\n。有示威者被打至血流披面，門牙飛脫，仍然被黑警按在地上，臉頰浸沒在自己流出的鮮血上。<br />\n<br />\n。在葵芳站內發射催淚彈槍，室內發放可導致人窒息死亡，指引亦明文寫明不能於室內使用。<br />\n<br />\n。在太古站內拘捕市民，期間追捕大量市民至扶手電梯，腳踢市民、將市民推落電材，險些「蘭桂芳」式發生人踩人奪命意外。另在站內一米「行刑式」開槍掃射示威者。<br />\n<br />\n。卧底黑警混入示威人群，並在黑警展開拘捕行動時制服前線示威者。過去多次衝擊極可能是由卧底黑警挑動造成，藉此抹黑示威者。<br />\n<br />\n。拘捕沒有示威裝束、手持電話作直播的社區主任，並涉嫌性騷擾以及暴力對待。<br />\n<br />\n還有很多令人振怒的濫權事件，難以詳述。香港人不斷被無日無之的暴力打壓，不禁感嘆到底我們為何會面對如此慘劇。這筆血債，林鄭月娥、香港政府、黑警處要如何償還？口講譴責暴力的達官貴人、社會賢達，又是否要繼續對黑警的戰爭罪行視而不見？<br />\n<br />\n沒有一位年青人會願意面對橡膠子彈、布袋彈、催淚彈。當中還有醫生、律師、各行各業專業人士站在戰地，有些可能只是拿著蒸餸碟或生理鹽水，焦急地想為香港付出。無人想在夏天面對槍林彈雨－－除了在香港生死存亡之際，他們願意將個人安危置之度外。<br />\n<br />\n這場仗一定要繼續，直至政府、黑警在制度中得到相應的懲罰，權力得到制衡。如此黑暗腐敗，無人能接受。"},{"pid":"8790bd36ea3fefaf86be501ed8c9917063a3658f","tid":1448284,"uid":90015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"求你地每個人都簽咗佢！<br />\n<br />\n請求美國派出醫療船支援香港 (10.Aug)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H221Iu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H221Iu&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=d641bd97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H221Iu</a><br />\n<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察<br />\n要求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 (10.Aug)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=45106b31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織（05.Aug)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzVVQB&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=a2319f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB</a><br />\n==================<br />\n<br />\n我講白啲，白宮聯署根本係本小利大，十萬人簽個名，白宮就要回應，佢就算唔回應，我哋都make 到noise畀傳媒造文章，根本無害。<br />\n<br />\n記得Confirmed Email！"},{"pid":"d922dfc8b8854888881ebd6be978b705e5dca145","tid":1448284,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c148030d76b81eadd5da46dfe47dff62488efc82","tid":1448284,"uid":294858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"有冇班法cosplay 警察<br />\n佢哋而家都冇號碼又冇委任証<br />\n有乜事就打返轉頭 或者拖到時間"},{"pid":"ee161d9559fa44e468c619a978ab8a40bcb7cc9d","tid":1448284,"uid":142803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf9bc52fe77cda906af676fa9d656acb78707a0d","tid":1448284,"uid":106255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df20201c5a3b6d83ce24ce82c87b3f63cca8df3","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"8.11  重點整理<br />\n<br />\n1. 警員對準遊行人士頭部發射，導致一女子永久失明<br />\n<br />\n2. 警員在葵芳、太古地鐵站內發射催淚彈，並於一米內開槍掃射示威者<br />\n<br />\n3. 北角福建幫毆打途人及記者，無人被捕。警黑勾結<br />\n<br />\n4. 警員亂棍毆打已被制服的示威者<br />\n<br />\n5. 警員假冒遊行人士，煽動示威者使用暴力<br />\n<br />\n6. 警員栽贜嫁禍示威者"},{"pid":"82cbf2240923ee3a9a4ea7925dc028916ad59552","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群好多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=5d4dee9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=867603d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"94d3cf7b2442530557ba90f663f3a8a08d9c2005","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HHpNtoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHHpNtoM.png&h=d3d91871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d53a4dbcd8a2cb7f4660a69dcc0de5b8d94d879","tid":1448284,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmDOcQy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmDOcQy.png&h=8caf558e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}